                    <ab>(S) In nomine sancte et individue Trinitatis. Anno ab incarnacione domini
                        nostri Iesu Christi .MCXVI.., VII. kalendas augusti, indicione nona.
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/2500">Odo</persName><rs
                            key="#Abbots"> abbas </rs><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii
                            </rs><orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/53">Sanctorum
                            Sixti et Fabiani</orgName> situm <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/43">Placencia</placeName>, communicato ecclesie fidelium
                            consilio<rs key="#City_assembly"> Placentinorum</rs> et<rs
                            key="#Village/castle_representatives"> Vuarstalensium</rs>, pro
                        multimoda caritatis humanitate et suarum pecuniarum largitate quam
                            tempore<persName key="#Abbesses" ref="#people/1601"> Imildis
                            </persName><rs key="#Abbesses">abbatisse </rs>ad terre beati Sixti iam
                        dudum perdite liberacione exhibuerunt, ad imitacionem eiusdem prenominate
                        abbatisse beate memorie, pactum et convencionem renovavit et confirmavit et
                            investivit<rs key="#Rural_communities"> homines </rs>de<placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Wood #Pigs #Sheep #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_groups #Operae #Transport_contracts #Albergaria/gifori #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#places/33"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Wood #Pigs #Sheep #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_groups #Operae #Transport_contracts #Albergaria/gifori #Tolls #Teloneum"
                                ref="#estates/40"> Vuarstalla </geogName></placeName>de <rs
                            key="#Tolls">ripatico</rs><rs key="#Rivers">
                            <placeName ref="#places/4196">Padi</placeName></rs> et <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludis</rs> cum partibus et omnes
                        Vuarstalenses <rs key="#Exemption">absolvit</rs> a ripatico et <rs
                            key="#Teloneum">toloneo</rs>, retento usibus ecclesie infrascripto
                        ripatico. Ceterum vero quod vocatur toloneum et <rs
                            key="#Transport_contracts">maltoletum</rs>
                        <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">concedimus</rs> hominibus de Vuastala<rs
                            key="#Consortes/shared_possessions"> in commune habendum</rs>. Insuper
                        statuit ut nulla iniuria vel violencia a se vel a suis successoribus vel a
                        suis hominibus inferatur alicui Vuarstalensium nec<rs key="#Castle"> in
                            castro</rs> nec<rs key="#Burgi"> in burgo</rs> nec <rs key="#Riverbed">
                            in ripa</rs> no<rs key="#Villas"> in villa</rs>. Et Vuarstalenses de
                        tabula casteli anualiter solvant<rs key="#Public_exactions"> unum
                            ramicinum</rs>, pro tabula burgi denarium unum curentis monete. Et si
                        iniuria ab altera parte alata fuerit, infra .xxx. dies consilio consulum
                        terre emendetur. Si qui curiales sunt seu burgenses qui velint retinere <rs
                            key="#Horses">equum</rs> convenientem armis et<rs key="#Armed_group">
                            arma </rs>et tenuerit ad terre, ecclesie suique libertatem tuendam
                        quicquid possident pro <rs key="#Feudum">feudo</rs> habeant cum omni<rs
                            key="#Honor"> honore</rs>. Rustici faciant <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Wine #Operae">braidam et vineam</rs>, dent <rs
                            key="#Pigs">porcum</rs> et <rs key="#Sheep">multonem</rs> tercium Â·et
                        quartum et spallam et amisere et <rs key="#Wood">plaustrum lignorum</rs> pro
                        unoquoque iugere, pro <rs key="#Albergaria/gifori">albergaria</rs> unum
                        sextarium vini, aliud grani meditas cuius sit frumenti, alia sit anona , et
                            <rs key="#Hay/fodder">stramen</rs> et lectum, et alia super imposita eis
                        non fiat. De <rs key="#Fluvial_transport">navi</rs> vero si inventa fuerit
                        in ripa habeat eundi et redeundi Placenciam. Concessit insuper communi
                        utilitati Vuarstalensium omnia <rs key="#Common_land">publica</rs> et
                        paludem et <rs key="#Forests">boscum</rs> et<rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"> pascua bestiarum</rs> e
                        Polisinos superiorem et inferiorem. Castrum et curtem prenominatus abbas nec
                        sui successores habeant licenciam nec potestatem dand alicui hominum sine
                        consilio duo( de )cim hominum, qui consules eligantur a populo qui etiam rem
                        populi dominique gubernent et regant. + Ego abbas Odo subscripsi et
                        confirmavi. Ego <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Gaitardus"
                                >Gaitardus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs> interfui
                        et subscripsi. Ego <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name>
                            Calvus </persName>presbiter et monacpus subscripsi. <rs key="#Witness"
                            >Testes</rs> roggati interfuerunt <persName>
                            <name ref="Berardus">Berardus</name> de Burgo</persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Bovus">Bovo </name>de Porta</persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Gherardus">Girardus </name></persName><rs
                            key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastal(dio),</rs>
                        <persName><name ref="Rotius">Rozo</name></persName>, item <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name> Bonus</persName>; <persName><name
                                ref="Truphus">Trufo</name>,</persName>
                        <persName><name ref="Grasulfus">Grasulfus,</name></persName>
                        <persName><name>Galeto</name></persName>,
                            <persName><name>Omnibene</name></persName>,
                            <persName><name>Agro</name></persName>, <persName>Gandoi(
                            nus)</persName>, <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martinus</name>
                            Bonagisus</persName>, <persName><name ref="Grimaldus"
                            >Grimaldus</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Sigefredus"
                                >Sigefredus</name></persName>. (S) Ego <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scriptor huius cartule concessionis post
                        traditam complevi </ab>
